RACE.FOOTNOTES: PATRIOTIC PARTY stalked early while off the inside, steadied sharply off the heels of NOTIMELIKEPRESENT when that one drifted in entering the turn, dropped back a few lengths then recovered to gain between runners mid turn, came three wide into the lane, closed in under a drive and gained a slim lead outside a pair of foes in mid stretch, drifted in some while dueling outside MISS YOU AJAX in the final sixteenth and held firm. MISS YOU AJAX , nudged off the rail in mid pack, dropped in and made a run to the inside of rivals mid turn, eased out and continued progress past the three sixteenths, drew on near even terms between runners in mid stretch, emerged in a battled inside the winner, was herded in towards the rail and kept on gamely. THRUSTER , well back early, progressed between rivals mid turn, altered to the rail to gain into the stretch, swung back out for room in mid stretch, straightened and closed well to quickly gain. STREET HUSTLE advanced along the rail to take command after a quarter mile, handled some outside pressure then cleared around the turn, widened a bit heading to the quarter pole, was taken on by a pair of foes leaving the three sixteenths, stayed on to about the sixteenth marker then faded. CAVALRY COMMAND sped to the early lead, was headed from the inside near the five eighths, forced the issue under a hearty ride mid turn, shifted out four wide into the lane and came up empty. NOTIMELIKEPRESENT , four then three wide early, drifted in bothering the winner entering the turn, circled four wide into the stretch but lacked a serious finish. JOHNSELECTRICRIDE broke slowly, lagged well back to mid turn, angled out soon after, shifted back in through the lane and had belated action. NOTION TO TAPIT saved ground near the half, angled out around the turn, went back in late and faded. HIS ROYAL G dropped back early, raced very wide into the stretch and failed to menace. HE ROLLS , four to five wide, chased and tired. NEVER SILENCED saved ground leaving the far turn and tired. PRESSING CONCERN , fractious in the gate, was squeezed back soon after the start, dropped in and rushed up toward the rail to be in range, angled out three wide leaving the three eighths, pursued, failed to kick on into the lane and faltered.
